unitName: Research conduct, analysis, write-up and submission
description: This is the final unit of two units designed to allow students to complete the conduct and write-up of a research project in the field of population health or clinical research. In this unit, students will complete the research project described in the research proposal developed in MPH5231. Students will interrogate data using acceptable analytical processes, and write-up the research project in a format and style suitable for publication in an academic setting.
faculty: Faculty of Medicine, Nursing and Health Sciences
